Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:06.34,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}In an era where the nations of the world\Nare silently fighting a war of intelligence,{In an era in which the nations of \Nthe world were waging a fierce war}
Comment: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:06.34,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}of information just out of sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:09.75,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}two countries were at odds with \Neach other: Ostania, in the east,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.03,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Westalis, in the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:16.08,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to keep an eye on the actions of \Na leading figure in Ostania's government
Comment: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:16.08,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}who was planning a war,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:19.84,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Westalis set Operation Strix in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.34,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one tasked with this operation \Nis the skilled agent, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.98,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mission given to the master of \Ndisguise with a hundred faces was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:29.26,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}to start a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:33.39,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}The father, Loid Forger, is a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:35.21,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}His true identity: a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:37.02,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Code name: Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:40.65,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mother, Yor Forger, is a civil \Nservant who works at city hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:43.34,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her true identity: an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:44.94,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Code name: Briar Rose. {changed from "Thorn Princess" because "Briar Rose" came up as a synonym for いばら姫. kaleido used this too but ive literally never heard this before}{K: いばら姫 is the common name for Sleeping Beauty in japanese, derived from the Grimm version which is known as Little Briar-Rose in English. i think it's a good localization}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:48.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}The daughter, Anya Forger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:51.32,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her true identity: a telepath \Nwho can read people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:53.91,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dog, Bond Forger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:58.08,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}His true identity: a canine seer \Nwho can see the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:01.47,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}As they maintain the facade\N of an ordinary family life,{They created this pretend \Nfamily for their own benefit,}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:05.88,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}they're each fighting their own battles \Nbehind closed doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:09.96,Default,opsync,0,0,0,,{opsync}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:00.46,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.19,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,The customers have been served.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:09.04,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll be heading home immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:15.03,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,My husband asked me \Nto buy milk and eggs on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:21.67,Default,Em,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit, that's the infamous assassin, Briar Rose!{Damn it... So she's the famous assassin \Nknown as the Thorn Princess...}{K: maybe drop "they call"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:23.02,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.10,Default,Em,0,0,0,,Die, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.74,Default,News,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}This just in: {K:: "this just in" would have been cool here, but probably too short?}{c:: the vibes don't feel right}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:43.75,Default,News,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}Several bodies believed to belong \Nto members of the Red Circus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.75,Default,News,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}have been found in a deserted building \Nin the Northern District.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:49.59,Default,News,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}The Red Circus, an extremist group \Nfunded by foreign interests,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:48.63,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:50.57,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I wanna watch cartoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:52.09,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,The news is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:52.80,Default,News,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}has committed numerous\Nindiscriminate acts of terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:52.80,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:57.33,Default,News,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}The authorities have concluded \Nthat the incident was caused
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:58.74,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's so much information I can get \Nout of just a single news broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.44,Default,News,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}by internal strife within the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.56,Default,News,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}Next up, we have stock market news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:04.63,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Okay, fine. You can change the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:07.20,Default,News,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}In today's stock market, \Nwe see a drastic decline
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.52,Default,News,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}compared to the figures from last week.{from where the numbers were \Nbefore the weekend...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.39,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,{\i0}Good day, Bondman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.53,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,{\i0}Your mission today is to \Ntail a certain target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:20.58,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}You need to find out where they're \Nkeeping their secret weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.45,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:23.92,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}and destroy it in order \Nto protect our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.92,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.54,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Yor—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:44.27,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Here—hngh—is the milk... and the eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:47.18,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Uh, thanks a bunch, Yor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.27,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Um, is something the matter?{idk if this sounds intentionally stiff in JP but it sounds stiff in english}{K: it's slightly polite, but not overly formal or anything. i'd replace it with something more natural/conversational}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:52.74,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:55.51,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I'm just a little... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:56.81,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:00.35,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can't know that while I was at work \NI went to an extremist hideout,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:03.70,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}killed all of them, \Nthen got shot in the butt by a straggler! {K:: would definitely prefer to keep the "in the butt" part somewhere around here, we only specify "butt" in the subs at 11:44 but she explicitly states it in this line}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.98,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been treated since then, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:11.06,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sh-She was shot with a gun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.01,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Are you going to die, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:18.22,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Anya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:19.40,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:24.73,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I've had a long day, though, \Nso I'm going to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:29.26,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surely I'll feel better... in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.63,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}after a good night's sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.63,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What the hell happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.74,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because I asked her to go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.76,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, that's gotta be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:48.81,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}We only got married \Nbecause the circumstances demanded it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:51.30,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}and making her run my errands upset her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.02,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom can survive a gunshot. {Mama won't die even if \Nshe's been shot with a gun.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.36,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:58.12,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm in deep, deep trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.57,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Any friction in our relationship jeopardizes the mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:03.50,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to do everything in my power \Nto remedy the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.32,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Daddy's super wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.95,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hopefully she'll be happier in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.68,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}It didn't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.68,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}It didn't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.07,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.91,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,G-Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.04,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.96,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to brighten her mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:35.54,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Yor! Since we're both off today,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.28,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,do you want to go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.55,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,A d-date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:45.55,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,I want to show my apprecation\Nfor all the work you put into our relationship.{I want to thank you for always helping \Nme with raising Anya and the chores.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.05,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,I wanna make today really special for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.51,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,A date...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.21,Default,Millie,0,0,0,,My boyfriend took me on a cruise the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.51,Default,Millie,0,0,0,,Have you gone on any dates recently, Yor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:59.60,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I've never been on one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:03.40,Default,Camilla,0,0,0,,Aren't you married? \NThere's no way you've {\i1}never{\i0} gone on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:06.36,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.56,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to get familiar with things like dating,{I must at least experience \Nthis thing they call a "date,"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:14.79,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}or people might start suspecting \Nthat we aren't a real family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:19.26,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Oh, we don't have to go if you don't feel like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.55,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:26.34,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I'm taking the opportunity\Nto learn as much as I can from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:27.55,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:31.13,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I'll go change right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.74,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I wanna come!{K: seems like kaleido used "I" for Anya's lines, while cyan used "Anya". either way is fine though imo. i think "Anya" is cuter}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.35,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Dates are so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:37.60,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you're staying home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.55,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,It's a date, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.36,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.27,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Sad face...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:44.19,Default,Bond,0,0,0,,Borf...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.99,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,All right, be good while we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:55.31,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,C'mere a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:01.32,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Listen, man! How many times do I need to say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:04.54,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,I'm an informant, not your errand boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:05.90,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,I don't have much of a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.66,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Anya isn't allowed to be home alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:12.65,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,and this is a very important mission \Nto ensure the stability of our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:15.69,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that you wanted \Nto create some new spy gadgets?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:17.92,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,I've already prepared you a cheque. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.86,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Can you stop giving me offers\Nthat I can't refuse?! {K: this sounds a bit stiff to me. maybe something more like "Stop taking advantage of me, you prick!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:25.11,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,All right, let's go, Yor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:33.89,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Ladies first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:41.65,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last night, I came up with 862 date plans \Nto {\i0}guarantee{\i1} she has fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:42.63,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I'll fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:50.43,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Um... I'm terribly sorry, Loid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:54.57,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll really hurt if I sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.14,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Could we just go for a walk, instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.07,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?! She's mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.51,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's still mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.65,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}This just ruined 794 of those plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:07.27,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,O-Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.58,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Sure, let's go for a little stroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.47,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:19.60,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Well damn, if his own kid is already worried,\Nit doesn't bode well for him.{K: looks like a misTL, he's talking about Loid specifically. also the "screwed" part is Loid being a failure of a spy, not the date itself being a failure, though i'm not sure if that changes the line}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.54,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Come on kiddo, let's go watch some cartoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.54,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Go, Bondman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.17,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Tail the target and protect world peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.90,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Scruffy Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:31.66,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:35.18,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I want to tail Mom and Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:44.22,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,What the hell? That sounds really freakin' cool! {or "That sounds far more fun!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:45.21,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.32,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Let's tail them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.36,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,But your old man's pretty sharp,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:52.24,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,so we're gonna have to be careful \Nand wear some disguises!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:53.01,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.97,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,You might be bringing even more \Nattention to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.85,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,No problemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.34,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:09.38,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,You've been charged with \Nguarding this house,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:13.38,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,highly skilled agents of the \NSecret Organization P2! {K: is this mistimed? this line ends with "bondo" when that should be part of the next line}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:18.63,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Bond, Director Chimera, \Nand Agent Penguinman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:32.10,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry about this Twilight,\Nbut there's no way I'm missing out{Listen here, Twilight. I'm using this opportunity \Nto check out the romance skills}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:34.66,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,{\i1}on seeing your fabled charisma{TL note: charisma means rizz} in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.57,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't read their minds.\NThey're too far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.93,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}What are those two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.84,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she pretending to be a spy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:46.78,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is that even fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:51.99,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever. I'll consider it as part of the mission\N and pretend I don't see them.
Comment: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:51.99,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}and pretend I haven't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:55.74,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Franky's with her, \Nso it's not like I have much to be concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:56.83,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Loid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.16,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Oh, er, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.58,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}More importantly,\NI need to brighten her mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:04.49,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Let's see what the mall has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:12.75,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,You have such a sleek figure, Yor. \NI think these would look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.61,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,How about trying it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.04,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I wore something that tight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:25.28,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}the pressure on the wound\Nwould definitely make me pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:26.62,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Absolutely not. {K: the way Yor phrases this is actually pretty rude; it comes off (to loid) as "no way (i'm wearing something like that.)" how about "I'd rather not."?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.21,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:36.40,Default,Movie Voice,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}Oh, my beloved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.56,Default,Movie Voice,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}Look me in the eyes and tell me you're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.56,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Yor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:43.94,Default,Movie Voice,0,0,0,,{\i0\an8}I won't let anyone else have \Nyour beautiful, proud soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:42.03,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,You're sticking out. Maybe you should sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:44.19,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Thanks, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.66,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I sit down, my butt'll hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:57.20,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I sit down, my butt'll hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:02.01,Default,Loid,750,75,0,,Yor, it isn't safe to stand here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:04.22,Default,Yor,625,10,0,,{\i1}But if I sit down, my butt'll hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:15.22,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:26.10,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.27,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.69,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't been focusing on the date at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:41.12,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've missed out on pretty much anything\NLoid was trying to teach me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.38,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:45.35,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her mood is even worse than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:47.54,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she just not like my date ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.30,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it?! What's going on in her head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.83,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I not do enough research?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:56.22,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Loid always tries to act cool, \Nbut he's absolutely choking the date right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:58.27,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,What a loser! {モジャジャジャ?}{K: he's using his own nickname as a laughing sound}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.37,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Scruffy Head, are you always this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:01.64,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:05.11,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,As someone who can't get any girls, \NI'm well in my rights to be making fun of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:05.85,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.67,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,What'd you say, you little—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:10.36,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're starting to get on my nerves. {K: nuance seems off here. i would TL this as "They're starting to annoy me/get annoying." }
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:12.98,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,It's been a long day. \NHow about we get dinner somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:13.74,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:20.47,Default,Host,0,0,0,,Ah, you must be Mister Forger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.11,Default,Host,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:43.22,Default,Host,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:45.67,Default,Host,0,0,0,,We have a strict dress code at our restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:50.68,Default,Host,0,0,0,,and we also do not allow guests under \Neighteen into our establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.05,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Well, you heard the guy. It's time to call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.78,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Let's head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.60,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,I was getting kinda bored anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:09.91,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-Is that Briar Rose?! What the hell is she doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:14.92,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,What's up? Needa use the bathroom or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.92,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:21.10,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:24.93,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the assassin who \Nraided our hideout yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.66,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:30.98,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the sole survivor of that tragedy, \NI took it as God's mercy on my soul. {K: a more accurate TL would be "As the sole survivor of that tragedy", but this is fine as well}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:33.28,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I took it as a sign to quit the underworld{I decided there and then \Nthat I'd quit the underworld}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:36.87,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}and focus on supporting my girlfriend,\Nbut this changes things! {K:: lit. has "supporting my girlfriend, and yet... (here she is!/she decides to show up!" consider specifying that}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:42.20,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clearly, there's only one thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:46.35,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna fucking murder her\Nfor what she did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.20,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a bad guy in the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.43,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,Die, Briar Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:52.75,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,Hurgh! I forgot you were the best assassin ever! \NI am defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:56.20,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Y-You're an assassin? Let's get a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.34,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,The Forgers are done.\NLet's get rid of Anya, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.88,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Let's get goin', kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:01.32,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.30,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Huh? You still wanna keep playing?{What? Are we still playing this game?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.23,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,My family's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.22,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:10.60,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she worried \Nabout her parents getting divorced or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.11,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,{\i1}She really feels that strongly\N about a pretend family?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:17.94,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,O-Okay, fine. \NI'll play with you a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.98,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Okay, our next game is called "Infiltration"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:21.94,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Infillytration! {K: she actually pronounces this correctly, but i like it better this way}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:25.00,Default,Waiter,0,0,0,,Would you like an aperitif?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.92,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,I'll have a glass of dry champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.95,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I'll just take a cocktail. Any is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:35.98,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Apparently they serve blowfish here, \Nwhich is a very rare delicacy from the far east.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.03,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,It's included in some of their meals, too. {(full) course meals(?)}{K: how about "one of their set menus"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:40.45,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I-Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:46.72,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Blowfish is highly poisonous, \Nbut I'm told its flesh is quite exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.39,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,Pardon, could you take this \Nto the lady at table 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.23,Default,Waiter,0,0,0,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:16:00.17,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just one sip of this and you'll be\Nmeeting your maker, Briar Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:02.02,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Scruffy Head, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.31,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,You can't rush this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:06.85,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,If you start getting sloppy,\Nthey're going to take notice.{We gotta be careful when we're infiltrating. \NGet too loud, and they'll find us.}{K:: prefer keeping the "we don't wanna get caught" nuance here}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.37,Default,Waiter,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:19.13,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Oh, my. This has quite a strong smell. {K:: i'm not sure if "fancy" is the right word here, i think it's more "unusual" or "interesting" i.e. she hasn't seen a drink with the color and especially the smell}{c:: the following line will do the legwork :muscle:}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:20.84,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,And it's so thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:24.61,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't touch that drink, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:40.15,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:44.65,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've avenged you, my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:49.45,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like the pain in my butt has gone away! \NI feel so much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:52.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a woman \Nwho'd built up an immunity to poisons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.70,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}My whole body feels a bit tingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.66,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:59.84,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I've really worked up an appetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:01.65,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I can't wait for the food to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.67,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Huh? Nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:07.67,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}What just happened? Is this because of the drink?{Is she in a better mood? \NIs it because of the drink?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:12.35,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? I'm pretty sure I put in enough to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:15.46,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}There's a fine line between poison and medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:19.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Ordinary people should take recommended doses\Nand follow directions when taking medicine.
Comment: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:19.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}and follow directions \Nwhen using medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:23.69,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:30.53,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time to take things into my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.70,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just finish her off myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:36.66,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should be able to build a makeshift \Nbomb with the stuff in storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.86,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that and that and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:43.71,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't be able to make a remote, \Nso I'll need to detonate it manually. {K:: remote here is lit. "timer", but i think it's an acceptable change}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.38,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:47.42,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope you can find it in your heart to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:51.77,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,We're coming up on the dining hall now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:55.72,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Once we're there, I'll lower you down on a wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:58.53,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Your job will be to listen \Nto what they're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:04.83,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should be able to make \Nthe bomb's body with **** and ****.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:07.04,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think they were stored on the right-hand shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:10.94,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}After I put in the blue **** \Non the opposite shelf and some ****.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.37,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}To make sure I get the most out of it,\N I'll need to include ****, too! {K: more literal TL would be "to make sure it's absolutely lethal"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:15.74,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,Okay, this should work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.30,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,Damn it! What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.56,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,Olive oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.93,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,Who the hell spilled all this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.93,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,I don't have time for this, damn it!
Comment: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:38.61,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,feels like this didn't need subbing?{Washtub!}{K: agreed}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:43.95,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,Who the hell set up a prank like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.94,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,This looks like the best thing\Nto fit my bomb in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:53.45,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,Actually, it might not be big enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.70,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, wait... what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.72,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,Why was there already a bomb in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.59,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,And what are these? Peanuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.66,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,A peanut bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:21.60,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:27.11,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they an ally of Briar Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:27.95,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.78,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}A kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.11,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Red Circus guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.00,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}She knows who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:42.72,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Consider this your warning. \NAn—We better not see your face ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.81,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Got it? There won't be a next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:50.36,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,You need to completely give up being a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:55.13,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Make Cathurin a happy lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.85,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}She even knows about Catherine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.37,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}She saw right through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:03.37,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}Briar Rose is a fearsome foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:07.97,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's got such an incredible kid \Nworking for her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.96,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}We live in completely different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.15,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not cut out for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:15.87,Default,Remnant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to forget this ever happened \Nand live a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:19.87,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,That was an oddly noisy restaurant...{I wonder what was going on \Nin the kitchen back there.} {K: she's not praising the restaurant, she's saying it was noisy/disquieting, with the explosion and all. maybe make it more clearly sarcastic? like "quite... lively."}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:22.32,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,The food was delicious, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:23.83,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:27.15,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank goodness. \NIt looks like she's feeling better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.95,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hopefully this ensures\Nthe harmony of the Forgers for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:36.65,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anya saves the day. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:39.97,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,So, hey... Where'd you run off to earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.94,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Loid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:57.36,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Ever since I was little, all of my time\N was dedicated to taking care of my brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.33,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,so I rarely ever had a chance to enjoy myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:03.99,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:08.39,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I really appreciate what you've done for me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:12.00,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I'd love to do this again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.96,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I'm not injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:19.15,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,I would love to. Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.95,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Oh, look! There's a traveling \Namusement park over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.98,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Let's check it out before it closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:34.29,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Can I ride the ferris wheel with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.57,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I wanna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:38.99,Default,Franky,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec!\NWhat happened to tailing them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.84,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:55.71,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}The medicine—that is, \Nthe poison—had worn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:58.92,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't understand women.
